#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pharmacy_retail.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To assign lot numbers, click on the product line. In the pop-up, specify the"
" lot number and the quantity against that lot number."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອລະບຸໝາຍເລກລ໋ອດ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໃສ່ລາຍການສິນຄ້າ. ໃນປັອບອັບ, ໃຫ້ລະບຸໝາຍເລກລ໋ອດ ແລະ ຈຳນວນສິນຄ້າສຳລັບ"
"ລ໋ອດນັ້ນ."

#. module: pharmacy_retail
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pharmacy_retail.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Upon validation of the receipt, the system automatically sets the locations (Racks) for the particular products received. \"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Acetratine 10 mg</font>” product will be stored at \"\n"
"            <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">WH/Stock/Rack 2</font>”."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອມີການຢືນຢັນການຮັບສິນຄ້າ, ລະບົບຈະກຳນົດຕຳແໜ່ງ (ຊັ້ນວາງ) ສຳລັບສິນຄ້າທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ສິນຄ້າ "
"\"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Acetratine 10 mg</font>” ຈະຖືກຈັດເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ \"\n"
"            <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">WH/Stock/Rack 2</font>”."

#. module: pharmacy_retail
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pharmacy_retail.welcome_article_body
msgid "Validate the reception for all quantities at once."
msgstr "ຢືນຢັນການຮັບສິນຄ້າສຳລັບຈຳນວນທັງໝົດໃນຄັ້ງດຽວ."

#. module: pharmacy_retail
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:pharmacy_retail.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບ! ຂໍໃຫ້ມ່ວນກັບການສຳຫຼວດ."

#. module: pharmacy_retail
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pharmacy_retail.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When a customer wants to purchase \"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Himalaya Baby Powder 100 g</font>,\" add \"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">3</font>\" quantity. When you select this product at that time, the system will fetch the\n"
"            price from the product master and enter the Lot Number \"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">A-003</font>\"."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອລູກຄ້າຕ້ອງການຊື້ \"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Himalaya Baby Powder 100 g</"
"font>,\" ໃຫ້ເພີ່ມຈຳນວນ \"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">3</font>\". ເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກສິນ"
"ຄ້ານີ້, ລະບົບຈະດຶງ\n"
"            ລາຄາຈາກຂໍ້ມູນຫຼັກສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ໃສ່ໝາຍເລກລ໋ອດ \"<font class=\"text-o-color-"
"1\">A-003</font>\" ໃຫ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: pharmacy_retail
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pharmacy_retail.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When the material is received, the user can either scan the barcode or "
"manually enter the Lot Number, Expiry Date and Quantity for \"<font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Acetratine 10 mg</font>” product received."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອໄດ້ຮັບສິນຄ້າ, ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດສະແກນບາໂຄດ ຫຼື ປ້ອນໝາຍເລກລ໋ອດ, ວັນໝົດອາຍຸ ແລະ ຈຳນວນ ສຳລັບສິນຄ້າ "
"\"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Acetratine 10 mg</font>” ທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບ."

#. module: pharmacy_retail
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pharmacy_retail.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While Processing the payment, the  customer gives  <font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">$200</font> as cash payment. Change amount as $8.41 gets "
"automatically calculated.  Validate the Order and Print Receipt."
msgstr ""
"ໃນຂະນະທີ່ດຳເນີນການຊຳລະເງິນ, ລູກຄ້າຈ່າຍ <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">$200</font> ເປັ"
"ນເງິນສົດ. ເງິນທອນຈຳນວນ $8.41 ຈະຖືກຄິດໄລ່ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ຢືນຢັນຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ ແລະ ພິມໃບຮັບເງິນ."

